ogy of an outflow cavity and the extended emission in\nthe [FeII] line at 1644 nm with the morphology of an edge-on disk. However, we\ndo not detect any large-scale jet from Gaia19bey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Aug 2020 23:15:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2020 21:26:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-14"}
