omated claustrum segmentation and thus yields\nconsiderable potential for facilitating MRI-based research of the human\nclaustrum. The software and models of our method are made publicly available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Aug 2020 07:25:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Aug 2021 09:30:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 May 2023 12:11:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-24"}
